title: Abbath - Count the Dead (Single) 2015 320ak
description:
Abbath (stylized as ABBATH) is a black metal band formed in 2015 by former Immortal guitarist and vocalist Abbath Doom Occulta after departing from Immortal earlier in 2015. 
The band is set to release their first album in 2016, and played live for the first time at Tuska Open Air 2015.
